# # ### Welcome to GitHub Page of Repository.
__**This page is the way I want to share your projects with anyone who wants my help. This page is a portfolio of all my work on Android. If anyone would like to edit the project would only have to create a new branch:**__

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git branch name_branch
$ git checkout name_branch
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
